{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782382843001,"sessionID":"ses_101b8caf5ffeN4H3YS4hZhe6E8","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"edit","callID":"tool_86RBx4zxznPe7Wm3IDHh5Scw","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-strategy.md","oldString":"## What Worked\n\n*To be appended per iteration.*\n\n## What Failed\n\n*To be appended per iteration.*\n\n## Exhausted Approaches\n\n*To be appended per iteration.*\n\n## Ruled-Out Directions\n\n*To be appended per iteration.*\n\n## Next Focus\n\nIteration 1: Survey the `designer-skills-main` 9-plugin taxonomy and the standalone doc titles to build a coarse candidate taxonomy.\n","newString":"## What Worked\n\n- Reading the CHANGELOG plus one skill per plugin quickly exposed the 9-plugin/97-skill discipline boundaries.\n\n## What Failed\n\n- None.\n\n## Exhausted Approaches\n\n- None.\n\n## Ruled-Out Directions\n\n- None.\n\n## Next Focus\n\nIteration 2: Deep-read the visual/style standalone docs (taste, delight, polish, soft, bolder, brutalist, minimalist, colorize, oklch) to refine the `sk-design-direction` / `sk-design-foundations` boundary.\n"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"diff":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-strategy.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-strategy.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-strategy.md\n@@ -48,21 +48,21 @@\n - Convergence threshold holds for consecutive low-yield iterations.\n \n ## What Worked\n \n-*To be appended per iteration.*\n+- Reading the CHANGELOG plus one skill per plugin quickly exposed the 9-plugin/97-skill discipline boundaries.\n \n ## What Failed\n \n-*To be appended per iteration.*\n+- None.\n \n ## Exhausted Approaches\n \n-*To be appended per iteration.*\n+- None.\n \n ## Ruled-Out Directions\n \n-*To be appended per iteration.*\n+- None.\n \n ## Next Focus\n \n-Iteration 1: Survey the `designer-skills-main` 9-plugin taxonomy and the standalone doc titles to build a coarse candidate taxonomy.\n+Iteration 2: Deep-read the visual/style standalone docs (taste, delight, polish, soft, bolder, brutalist, minimalist, colorize, oklch) to refine the `sk-design-direction` / `sk-design-foundations` boundary.\n","filediff":{"file":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-strategy.md","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-strategy.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-strategy.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-strategy.md\n@@ -48,21 +48,21 @@\n - Convergence threshold holds for consecutive low-yield iterations.\n \n ## What Worked\n \n-*To be appended per iteration.*\n+- Reading the CHANGELOG plus one skill per plugin quickly exposed the 9-plugin/97-skill discipline boundaries.\n \n ## What Failed\n \n-*To be appended per iteration.*\n+- None.\n \n ## Exhausted Approaches\n \n-*To be appended per iteration.*\n+- None.\n \n ## Ruled-Out Directions\n \n-*To be appended per iteration.*\n+- None.\n \n ## Next Focus\n \n-Iteration 1: Survey the `designer-skills-main` 9-plugin taxonomy and the standalone doc titles to build a coarse candidate taxonomy.\n+Iteration 2: Deep-read the visual/style standalone docs (taste, delight, polish, soft, bolder, brutalist, minimalist, colorize, oklch) to refine the `sk-design-direction` / `sk-design-foundations` boundary.\n","additions":5,"deletions":5},"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-strategy.md","time":{"start":1782382842996,"end":1782382842999}},"id":"prt_efe4bc0c1001KV4slh7uIVcUJh","sessionID":"ses_101b8caf5ffeN4H3YS4hZhe6E8","messageID":"msg_efe4bae3b001osw2jBvolvAizv"}}
