/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-dashboard.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-dashboard.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-dashboard.md\n@@ -5,16 +5,17 @@\n | run | focus | newInfoRatio | findings count | status |\n | --- | ----- | ------------ | -------------- | ------ |\n | 1 | Survey designer-skills-main 9-plugin taxonomy and standalone doc titles | 1.0 | 4 | complete |\n | 2 | Visual/style standalone docs and the direction/foundations boundary | 0.85 | 4 | complete |\n+| 3 | Motion/animation corpus and the scope of sk-design-motion | 0.75 | 4 | complete |\n \n ## Question Status\n \n 0/5 answered\n \n ## Trend\n \n-Last 2 ratios: 1.0 → 0.85\n+Last 3 ratios: 1.0 → 0.85 → 0.75\n \n ## Dead Ends\n \n None.\n@@ -24,5 +25,5 @@\n None.\n \n ## Next Focus\n \n-Iteration 3: Read the motion/animation standalone docs and designer-skills motion/interaction skills to scope `sk-design-motion`.\n+Iteration 4: Read critique/accessibility/quality standalone docs and designer-skills visual-critique/prototyping-testing skills to scope `sk-design-critique`.\n","additions":3,"deletions":2},"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1782385908281,"end":1782385908286}},"id":"prt_efe7a7e06001r6YIdsUTp6VVRy","sessionID":"ses_101b8caf5ffeN4H3YS4hZhe6E8","messageID":"msg_efe7a6cd6001Mzs2gsMSwDRNaP"}}
