: \".opencode/skills/sk-design-md-generator/assets/design_md_prompt_template.md\",\n        \"source\": \"derived\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"name\": \"cardinal_rules_card\",\n        \"kind\": \"reference\",\n        \"path\": \".opencode/skills/sk-design-md-generator/assets/cardinal_rules_card.md\",\n        \"source\": \"derived\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"causal_summary\": \"sk-design-md-generator captures a live website's real, measured CSS into a publication-quality v3 Style Reference DESIGN.md so AI agents build against ground truth instead of hallucinating colours, fonts, spacing, and shadows. It ships an embedded TypeScript pipeline under backend/ that runs a three-phase pipeline: EXTRACT (a Playwright crawler samples five viewports and emits output/<domain>/tokens.json with every token tagged a 4-layer stability class), WRITE (the agent composes the v3 Style Reference DESIGN.md copying every numeric value verbatim from tokens.json, 6-digit lowercase hex, L1+L2 in main sections, L3 marked subject-to-change, L4 excluded; the value-bearing sections are pre-rendered deterministically, so the agent writes prose only), and VALIDATE (validate.ts checks hex accuracy and section completeness). The cardinal rule is verbatim fidelity: a value that is estimated, rounded, or invented breaks the document's whole reason to exist. It is the extraction-and-format-fidelity engine of the sk-design-* family - sibling to sk-design-interface (which invents new distinctive direction) and the mcp-figma / mcp-open-design transports (which source from Figma and Open Design rather than live URLs) - and its DESIGN.md is the implementation contract sk-code builds against. Setup is a one-time cd backend && npm install && npx playwright install chromium.\",\n    \"source_docs\": [\n      \"SKILL.md\",\n      \"README.md\",\n      \"INSTALL_GUIDE.md\",\n      \"references/extraction_workflow.md\",\n      \"references/troubleshooting.md\",\n      \"changelog/v1.0.0.0.md\",\n      \"assets/design_md_prompt_template.md\",\n      \"assets/cardinal_rules_card.md\"\n    ],\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-06-21T10:00:00Z\",\n    \"last_updated_at\": \"2026-06-21T10:00:00Z\"\n  }\n}","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":158,"totalLines":158,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/skills/sk-design-md-generator/graph-metadata.json","time":{"start":1782386031330,"end":1782386031339}},"id":"prt_efe7c786a001nmqAJtxJMF8suw","sessionID":"ses_101b8caf5ffeN4H3YS4hZhe6E8","messageID":"msg_efe7c5172001wNBAYAlvmeiRo0"}}
