{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782386112335,"sessionID":"ses_101b8caf5ffeN4H3YS4hZhe6E8","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"tool_DeSE8x8WQ3bDfXcxtueKvCx2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Deep Research Dashboard — kimi27 lineage\n\n## Iteration Table\n\n| run | focus | newInfoRatio | findings count | status |\n| --- | ----- | ------------ | -------------- | ------ |\n| 1 | Survey designer-skills-main 9-plugin taxonomy and standalone doc titles | 1.0 | 4 | complete |\n| 2 | Visual/style standalone docs and the direction/foundations boundary | 0.85 | 4 | complete |\n| 3 | Motion/animation corpus and the scope of sk-design-motion | 0.75 | 4 | complete |\n| 4 | Critique, accessibility, and quality-corpus clustering | 0.70 | 5 | complete |\n| 5 | Parent structural model — hub with nested packets vs. umbrella router | 0.65 | 7 | complete |\n\n## Question Status\n\n1/5 answered\n\n## Trend\n\nLast 3 ratios: 0.75 → 0.70 → 0.65\n\n## Dead Ends\n\nNone.\n\n## Blocked Stops\n\nNone.\n\n## Next Focus\n\nIteration 6: Map the existing `sk-design-interface` and `sk-design-md-generator` skills into the proposed children and define backward-compatibility/onboarding implications.\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-dashboard.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-dashboard.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1782386112326,"end":1782386112333}},"id":"prt_efe7da38c001nTnvCMD9W7DD28","sessionID":"ses