{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782386203987,"sessionID":"ses_101b8caf5ffeN4H3YS4hZhe6E8","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"tool_Gq3NLLq70CsVx3agOb3MY6P5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Deep Research Dashboard — kimi27 lineage\n\n## Iteration Table\n\n| run | focus | newInfoRatio | findings count | status |\n| --- | ----- | ------------ | -------------- | ------ |\n| 1 | Survey designer-skills-main 9-plugin taxonomy and standalone doc titles | 1.0 | 4 | complete |\n| 2 | Visual/style standalone docs and the direction/foundations boundary | 0.85 | 4 | complete |\n| 3 | Motion/animation corpus and the scope of sk-design-motion | 0.75 | 4 | complete |\n| 4 | Critique, accessibility, and quality-corpus clustering | 0.70 | 5 | complete |\n| 5 | Parent structural model — hub with nested packets vs. umbrella router | 0.65 | 7 | complete |\n| 6 | Mapping existing skills and backward-compatibility/onboarding implications | 0.60 | 5 | complete |\n\n## Question Status\n\n3/5 answered\n\n## Trend\n\nLast 3 ratios: 0.70 → 0.65 → 0.60\n\n## Dead Ends\n\nNone.\n\n## Blocked Stops\n\nNone.\n\n## Next Focus\n\nIteration 7: Final taxonomy refinement, corpus-source assignment per child, and convergence check before synthesis.\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-dashboard.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-dashboard.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/kimi27/deep-research-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1782386203982,"end":1782386203986}},"id":"